StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [sp_GetDischargeCode]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@SSN as varchar(9), @DischargeCode as varchar(4) output AS
SELECT @DischargeCode = C.DISCHARGE_CODE FROM PERSON P, NWA, CONTRACT C WHERE P.SOCIAL_SECURITY_NUMBER = @SSN AND P.PERSON_ID = NWA.MARINE_CANDIDATE_ID AND NWA.NWA_ID = C.NWA_ID
